<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM16">
<l>puṇṇiyaṅkaḷ ceytaṉavum poynneṟikkaṭ cārāmē</l>
<l>yeṇṇiyō raintu micaintaṉavā ṟiṇṇiya</l>
<l>kaimmāvi ṉīrurivai mūvuruvum pōrttukanta</l>
<l>vammāṉuk kāṭpaṭṭa vaṉpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They have done meritorious deeds and, meditating</l>
<l>without approaching false paths, all the five [senses] have agreed</l>
<l>in the love for which [I] became a servant to the lord</l>
<l>who rejoiced in covering [his] three forms in the wet hide of the animal with the firm hand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
